track_notes:
I parked in the village Srednji vrh. There is a parking as you enter the village (https://maps.app.goo.gl/tX3p2ZH8cQ32w8Tj8). 

First few kilometers of the trail is quite decent forest road, but driving is allowed only to the land lords. It is your call. I walked.

Attached GPS track covers only my descent. This is what I would recommend also for the ascent. My ascent was full of detours and learning from mistakes :-)

Descent took me 3h15m. My estimation for the ascent would be 4h15m without detours.
track_title: From Srednji vrh following the Hladnik creek
